HL7_v2 is the most widely plemented healthcare standard in the world. 95% of US healthcare organizations use it and more than 35 countries have V2 implementations.
This is especially true in the exchange of orders, results, admission/discharge/transfer (ADT) and public health communication.

v2 is very dense

